Fellow Posters. CHECK THIS OUT:<br>
aka DR. CRAZY STRIKES A BLOW FOR VIET VETERANS - POV SITE - IN SAN FRANCISCO:<br><br>
&quot;a major story came out in sunday's SF Chronicle/Examiner.  lead sentence:<br><br>
&quot;Log on to the Internet, type out www.pbs.org/pov/stories, and watch the transformation of Dr. Barry Spatz of Irvine from anti-war firebrand to advocate for an honest dialogue with Vietnam vets.&quot;   Really, I did not make this up.<br><br>
Well, shucks, brothers and sisters, I didn't know I was transformed. I just learned that you guys, and gals, were more than just bums asking for money at the freeway on ramps&quot; - &quot;Homeless, Helpless, Viet Nam Vet, God Bless&quot; usually said the piece of cardboard.  Now I know more. But, those creep on the on ramps don't, cause they are still there, doing the bum thing.<br><br>
It is time to wake up, and shake up this site, to rock and roll, to move and groove, to get back to the business of IN YOUR FACE.  So Chet, So Art, So DocDel, So Tanker, So Betty who won't post, and to all of you, get on board, cause this is OUR train, and I will be GOD DAMN if I let it run out of steam  (whooooeie, that took a lot of steam...and I am now out of it, steam that is)<br><br>
Good nite Viet Nam<br><br>
